            "effect": "The deluded mob uses their fists, wooden planks, and anything else they can pick up to attack each enemy in a 5-foot emanation with fervor, if not coordination (DC 18 basic Reflex save). The damage depends on the number of actions.  \n [#] 1d8 piercing or bludgeoning damage  \n [##] 1d8+6 piercing or bludgeoning damage  \n [###] 2d8+6 piercing or bludgeoning damage",
