              }
            ],
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "When they feel cornered, the mob lashes out more recklessly. While the deluded mob is flanked, Flail Desperately and Throw Detritus are DC 17 and deal an additional 2 damage per action spent on the activity.",
            "type": "stat_block_section"
